  Band pass-through – 15\n• Crossover Symmetry activation\n\nSPRINT WORK\
 n• 10 yd sprint – 4 reps\n• 20 yd sprint – 3 reps\n• 40 yd sprint – 3 re
 ps\n• Full recovery: 2–3 minutes between full-speed reps\n\nPLYOMETRICS\
 n• Depth jump – 4 x 3\n• Broad jump – 4 x 2\n• Lateral bound – 3 x 3/sid
 e\n\nSTRENGTH\n• Trap Bar Deadlift – 6 x 2 @ RPE 7–8\n• Pull-ups or assi
 sted pull-ups – 3 x 6–8\n• Chest-supported DB row – 3 x 8\n• 1-arm DB ro
 w – 3 x 8/side\n• Face pull – 3 x 15\n• Farmer carry – 3 x 30–40 yd\n\nB
