 player: 20–25 controlled flat-ground throws focused on mechanics\n• No m
 ax-effort pitching when sore or after a game-heavy week\n\nTRACKING\nRec
 ord weight used\, sets/reps completed\, RPE\, sprint times when measured
 \, soreness\, and notes.\nPain rule: stop any exercise or throw that cau
 ses sharp pain.
